  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">

    <div class="subcontent">

      <h2>Welcome to the Bartendventory App</h2>

      <p>With this app, you will be able to create/or edit a cabinet that you will be able to fill from a list of liquors.
      If a particular liquor is not available, you will be able to create a liquor. The main idea is to be able to build an
      inventory sheet for all alcohol in your cabinet.</p>
      

    </div>
    
  

   
